            </p>
            <p class="text-mist leading-relaxed">
              You don't <span class="text-cyan">NEED</span> my setups to become profitable!
              If you've already spent years developing your own trading setups and the bottleneck is non-technical,
              the Treehouse is probably your best bet. Maybe you're closer than you think.
            </p>
          </div>
